{"tid":298124,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"男人既浪漫原於對Pizza既熱愛","createTime":"2017-06-26T04:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T10:40:05.000Z","uid":44458,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af6d84aa40675082c507921689c1816936606411","tid":298124,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T04:58:34.000Z","msg":"因為平時成日食Pizza實在太熱愛，愛佢自然要做出來<br />\n所以最近都努力學整pizza, 原來好簡單又快, 自己鐘意乜料都得 <br />\n呢D先係男人既浪漫, 上次講開有人話無焗爐, 其實買個細細個230度都夠晒用,<br />\nPizza底粉整完可以切\b開粉整定幾個波波放冰格, 隋時用得 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/26/125125_4efdd2f969559e8b1c92e99f32ded48e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F26%2F125125_4efdd2f969559e8b1c92e99f32ded48e.jpg&h=37a6cf87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住放茄膏或千島都係隨你喜歡, Default都係茄膏加鹽加黑椒 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/26/125130_3fb5ed13afe8714a7e5d13ee506003dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F26%2F125130_3fb5ed13afe8714a7e5d13ee506003dd.jpg&h=7fb0e586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n加料同芝士, 我加煙肉同大腸唔鐘意放大多芝士, 千島夏威夷先大量芝士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/26/125136_f99687dd719c4e8bc6a39e946c3d9ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F26%2F125136_f99687dd719c4e8bc6a39e946c3d9ef7.jpg&h=2c45517d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n230度 呢塊有影相既就10分鐘, 我平時鐘意膿D就11-12分鐘"},{"pid":"01700f2d981e8e99f0437d65b8eccd31e3a42212","tid":298124,"uid":11980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"賣相ok喎屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218f5e8b936c3eabbab2e61587a878523be67658","tid":298124,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:35:49.000Z","msg":"個底用咩整？超市有冇現成買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc56b1475942b7d8ef96af31e9fe97ffcc5b72b","tid":298124,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"大腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無豬皮羅白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bb9598703484d91da139a67d157b2e3783653c","tid":298124,"uid":74908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b82a174394f0c7e5b1ea721c63566141fda358","tid":298124,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"整北京鴨 pizza <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6247aad481af0bceabc8e127e095b66af64ecd","tid":298124,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T06:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個底用咩整？超市有冇現成買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高根粉, 或日本有個&quot;強&quot;字麵粉，一樣做法，做硬底唔洗等太耐，我copy個做法比你<br />\n<br />\n和暖水（不超過 40C / 105F） 125毫升<br />\n糖 1/2茶匙<br />\n快速酵母 1茶匙<br />\n橄欖油（或沙拉油）3茶匙<br />\n高筋粉 200克<br />\n鹽 1/2茶匙<br />\n<br />\n快速酵母 1茶匙 同暖水溝左先，再放一齊初埋佢達下佢就得<br />\n<br />\n500g 可做6個波波，有隻日本仲平過大陸麵粉，1kg 唔洗$40 做到12塊!!"},{"pid":"9841107ab0550eee13f2edeca671c5249ce8bc4e","tid":298124,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T06:45:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整北京鴨 pizza <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個我真係想試，下之試左加煙肉同叉燒先再報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b943b8e0cd2d057c6c59809dd68a9fed8c4d14b","tid":298124,"uid":4846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T06:59:25.000Z","msg":"麵粉係惠康百佳搵到？<br />\n留名得閒試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe65ab6c48e607d1b729943a9c1c49bb7b6aab3c","tid":298124,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T07:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麵粉係惠康百佳搵到？<br />\n留名得閒試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸個隻$20 500g<br />\n<br />\n其實都一樣不過有made in japan更係唔買支那貨<br />\n<br />\n惠康百佳吉次島度度都有齊要買既野, 茄膏買支裝方便D"},{"pid":"3431c21e4802aee202af1c468306c593efd8187e","tid":298124,"uid":72481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T09:22:35.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"54a894b033c2ce94b973a4e7cd417c37cbb6917d","tid":298124,"uid":22313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}